{"article_id":"A2lPaohAXB8XXoKE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"On Wednesday","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Education Secretary Betsy DeVos","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Elizabeth","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"( Betsy )","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Dee DeVosMichigan Republican Senate candidate notes places","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"' I disagree with ' Trump 's Campaign Report :","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Biden 's virtual campaign swings through Florida 's Morning Report","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"- Presented by Facebook -","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"In reversal , Trump says","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"he wo n't disband coronavirus task force","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"MORE issued final rules","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"on how all schools will address allegations of sexual misconduct ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"securing new protections for students and faculty","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"accused of misconduct .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"The new rules modify Title IX , a 1972 law","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"prohibiting \" discrimination","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"based on sex in education programs or activities","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"that receive Federal financial assistance , \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"narrowing the definition of sexual harassment","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"and requiring schools to challenge evidence","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and cross-examine students via a live hearing , among other things detailed in the more than 2,000-page rule .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"The new regulations ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"which take effect in August ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"will only find schools in violation of Title IX","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"if they are determined to be \" deliberately indifferent \" to accusations of sexual assault","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that occurred in their programs and activities .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"`` Too many students have lost access to their education","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"because their school inadequately responded","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"when a student filed a complaint of sexual harassment or sexual assault , ''","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"DeVos said in a statemnet .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"`` This new regulation requires schools to act in meaningful ways","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"to support survivors of sexual misconduct ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"without sacrificing important safeguards","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"to ensure a fair and transparent process .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"We can and must continue to fight sexual misconduct in our nation 's schools ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and this rule makes certain","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that fight continues . ''","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"President Trump","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Donald John TrumpTrump says","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Chuck Todd should be fired over edited clip of Barr","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Trump lashes out at Obama in Mother 's Day tweetstorm","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Georgia officials :","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Arrest made over online threat against Ahmaud Arbery protesters","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"MORE issued a statement","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"describing the new regulations as \" even-handed justice \" with \" a transparent grievance process","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"that treats the accused as innocent until proven guilty . \"","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"\" With today ' s action and every action","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to come ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"the Trump administration will fight for America ' s students , \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Trump said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"DeVos and the Trump administration have been critical of Title IX ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"they have said","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"unjustly puts matters of sexual assault and harassment in the hands of education officials .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Republicans were critical of the Obama administration ' s use of Title IX ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"which","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"they argue","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"lacked public input .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"\" This final rule respects and supports victims","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"and preserves due process rights for both the victim and the accused , \"","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"Sen. Lamar Alexander Andrew","depth":16},{"id":61,"text":"( Lamar )","depth":16},{"id":62,"text":"Lamar AlexanderSen .","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"Lamar Alexander to self-quarantine","depth":15},{"id":64,"text":"after staff member tests positive for COVID-19 Administration health officials to answer senators ' questions via videoconferencing","depth":15},{"id":65,"text":"Alexander :","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"People will return to work","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"if they know","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"those around them are being tested","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"MORE","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"( R-Tenn. ) ,","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"chairman of the Senate Education Committee ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"said in a statement .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"\" Under the previous administration , a single official in the U.S. Department of Education was issuing edicts ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"without the proper public input ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"to 6,000 colleges and universities about how to handle the complex and sensitive problem of sexual assault on college campuses , \"","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Alexander added .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Victim advocacy groups , such as Know Your IX , have said","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"that the new rules are `` rolling back the rights of student survivors , ''","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"claiming","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"they shield schools from liability for sexual misconduct","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"that takes place in their facilities .","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"`` If this rule goes into effect ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"it will make schools more dangerous","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"and could push survivors out of school entirely , ''","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"the group tweeted .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Fatima Goss Graves , president of the National Women ' s Law Center , told The New York Times","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"the organization plans to contest the new rules in court .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"\" Betsy DeVos and the Trump administration are dead set on making schools more dangerous for everyone","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"- even during a global pandemic , \"","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Goss Graves told the Times .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"\" And","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"if this rule goes into effect ,","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"survivors will be denied their civil rights","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"and will get the message loud and clear","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"that there is no point","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"in reporting assault . \"","depth":15}],"relations":[{"parent":193,"left":0,"right":192,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":192,"left":105,"right":191,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":1,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":99,"right":103,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":4,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":98,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":5,"right":102,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":100,"right":101,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":191,"left":132,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"l